      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan documented; version control and issue tracking in place; regression test suite covers solver modules used in hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is maintained under a formal SQA plan with Git-based version control, automated regression testing covering all turbulence and scalar transport modules, and documented issue resolution logs. Required and achieved levels are equal at Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
