      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to Navier-Stokes and scalar transport equations; observed order of accuracy within 10% of formal order.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification confirms second-order spatial accuracy for momentum and first-order for hemolysis scalar transport. Observed orders are 1.92 and 0.97 respectively, within tolerance. Code verification is complete at the required gradation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
